4.7. Export Minister Directory

  


Requirements

This will export all living ordained ministers using the following report:

  


  * Minister or Deacon ("M" if a minister; "D" if a Deacon)
  * Full Name
  * Minister or Deacon Ordination Year
  * Bishop ("B" if a Bishop)
  * Bishop Ordination Year
  * Church Name (from Church #)



  


This should be sorted by:

  * Year Ordained (earliest year)
  * Ministry Role (first Bishop, then Minister, then Deacon)
  * Age (oldest first)
